    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>发挥聪明才智逃脱吧！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Another Door是引导大家进入有固有故事和令人毛骨悚然的挑战的投入感环境的VR密室逃脱游戏。 从充满怪才科学家制造的陷阱的藏身之处到被死去的孩子的灵魂诅咒的幽灵出现的玩偶的房间,再到幻觉模糊现实的秘密实验室,每个插曲都传递着新鲜、刺激的悬疑故事!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216330/extras/573822a9ebfdfeecb594b825b049f319.poster.avif?t=1737697230\" width=800 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216330/extras/573822a9ebfdfeecb594b825b049f319.webm?t=1737697230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216330/extras/573822a9ebfdfeecb594b825b049f319.mp4?t=1737697230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Another Door通过真正的虚拟现实投入感,再现真实密室逃脱的刺激。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216330/extras/79f6356201a68ccb82676b797e0e76f2.poster.avif?t=1737697230\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216330/extras/79f6356201a68ccb82676b797e0e76f2.webm?t=1737697230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216330/extras/79f6356201a68ccb82676b797e0e76f2.mp4?t=1737697230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主要特征 :</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - 寻找隐藏在各处的收藏品吧</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - 用我自己的拼图体验这5个独特的主题吧</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - 沉浸式音响设计</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - 联机联机</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>远远超过看得见地</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Another Door提供了五个独特的插曲，每个插曲都有新的主题、故事和拼图机制。 玩家可以选择插曲，就像在图书馆里选择书籍一样，所以两个冒险感觉不一样。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216330/extras/d2d653a477fdb5fbb043582c8901c897.poster.avif?t=1737697230\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216330/extras/d2d653a477fdb5fbb043582c8901c897.webm?t=1737697230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216330/extras/d2d653a477fdb5fbb043582c8901c897.mp4?t=1737697230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一个人或者和朋友一起玩吧！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了体验令人毛骨悚然的体验，请独自进行比赛或最多与3名朋友组队，共同解决最难的课题。 探索逃生期间，利用语音聊天共享线索，实时配合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>拼图测试</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论是一个人还是和朋友一起面对未知世界的Another Door,将悬念、团队合作、精神推向极限,带来充满复杂拼图的令人难忘的VR冒险。</p>",
